OL,3,CFarmer says relentless wet weather has
OL,4,Cleft his crops 'rotting in the ground'
OL,6,FA Wiltshire farmer says the prolonged
OL,7,Fwet weather has destroyed many of his
OL,8,Fcrops.
OL,10,FTom Collins said that the conditions
OL,11,Fthis winter on his Malmesbury farm
OL,12,Fhave been the worst he has ever
OL,13,Fwitnessed and that it could take
OL,14,Fmonths for the land to recover.
OL,16,FEarlier this month, the government
OL,17,Fannounced farmers would be eligible
OL,18,Ffor grants of up to #25,000 to help
OL,19,Frestore land damaged by flooding.
