OL,3,CFarmer says relentless wet weather has
OL,4,Cleft his crops 'rotting in the ground'
OL,6,FThe issue of flooding is hitting both
OL,7,Farable and livestock farming, with
OL,8,Fcrops either rotting or not able to be
OL,9,Fplanted, while grass and feed for
OL,10,Fanimals is underwater.
OL,12,FMr Collins said: "It has just been
OL,13,Fawful, it started raining in October
OL,14,Fand hasn't stopped since.
