OL,3,CFarmer says relentless wet weather has
OL,4,Cleft his crops 'rotting in the ground'
OL,6,F"We've had flooding across the farm,
OL,7,Fall our grassland has been under the
OL,8,Fwater for long periods of time and
OL,9,Fthat brings rubbish down, we've had to
OL,10,Fgo litter-picking and it's ripped
OL,11,Fthrough all the fencing, that's pretty
OL,12,Fbad.
OL,14,F"Then on the arable side we've got
OL,15,Fcrops that are just missing, the
OL,16,Fground has set wet all winter and the
OL,17,Fcrops have just rotted away in the
OL,18,Fground."
