OL,3,CFarmer says relentless wet weather has
OL,4,Cleft his crops 'rotting in the ground'
OL,6,FIt has prompted warnings that some
OL,7,Ffarms may not have a harvest for the
OL,8,Ffirst time since the Second World War.
OL,10,FFields have been left underwater
OL,11,Ffollowing record amounts of rainfall
OL,12,Fand 11 named storms since September.
OL,14,FWheat yields are expected to drop by
OL,15,F15% and winter barley down 22%,
OL,16,Fprompting a warning from the National
OL,17,FFarmers Union that it will lead to
OL,18,Fprice rises for consumers.
