OL,3,CFarmer says relentless wet weather has
OL,4,Cleft his crops 'rotting in the ground'
OL,6,FFarming Minister Mark Spencer said:
OL,7,F"We want to make sure the Farming
OL,8,FRecovery Fund offers the support
OL,9,Ffarmers need to recover from
OL,10,Funinsurable damage.
OL,12,F"It's why we've immediately listened
OL,13,Fand responded to feedback on the
OL,14,Flaunch of the initial phase of the
OL,15,Fscheme.
OL,17,F"This means that farmers will be able
OL,18,Fto receive payments for all land
OL,19,Fparcels which are flooded contiguous
OL,20,Fto an eligible river.
