OL,3,CFarmer says relentless wet weather has
OL,4,Cleft his crops 'rotting in the ground'
OL,6,FAnd Professor Cannon fears this is
OL,7,Fgoing to be an ongoing trend because
OL,8,Fof climate change.
OL,10,F"This time last year we were talking
OL,11,Fabout a wet spring impacting crop
OL,12,Festablishment and we are back here
OL,13,Fagain just a year later", she added.
